      "title": "One day service for Passports to commence in 3 more districts",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The \u2018One Day Service\u2019 for issuing of passports will commence in three more districts from next Monday (June 04), according to Minister Dhammika Perera.",
        "Accordingly, the One Day Service will also be carried out at the Immigration and Emigration Department\u2019s regional offices at Kandy, Matara and Vavniya from Monday."
      ],
